---
title: Pineapple Pork Rice Bowls With Snow Peas, Carrots, and Thai Basil Rice
description: Get into a tropical groove with this recipe that’s a little sweet, a little savory, and all-around lick-your-lips good. It centers around pork chops cooked with cubes of sweet, golden pineapple. But the adventure doesn’t stop there—it continues into the snow peas and carrots tossed with gingery moo shu spice. It’s all served next to Thai basil rice, which completes this dish’s palette of fantastically fun flavors.
